= SET _key1_ _value1_  _key2_ _value2_ ... _keyn_ _valuen_ (Redis >= 1.1) DRAFT =
_Time complexity: O(1)_ for each _key_

 Set the string _ nth value_ as value of the _ nth key_.
 Each string can't be longer than 1073741824 bytes (1 GB).

== Return value ==

[ReplyTypes Status code reply]

== See also ==
 * [SetCommand MSETNX] is like SET but it only take one key value pair.
 * [MsetnxCommand MSETNX] is like MSET but doesn't perform the operation if the _any_ target key already exists.
